author: Luc Olinga
title: Bitcoin Hits $122K but Something Feels Off
description: The world’s most famous cryptocurrency just hit a new all-time high, but don’t call it a comeback just yet.
content:
Bitcoin is on the move again.
The worlds largest cryptocurrency by market value surged past a symbolic milestone on Wednesday, reaching a record-breaking $122,055 on the Coinbase exchange around 3:5… [+2594 chars]
